{"tid":956124,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"正式宣佈：當勞侵正式就任牛軍大都督","createTime":"2018-12-26T04:34:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T13:03:12.000Z","uid":54870,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"908bf782581a594b6b8de2362fca02ef6b2e0847","tid":956124,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:34:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1545795482635&amp;issue=20181226\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1545795482635%26issue%3D20181226&d=nlZSAbnHmEPvOkfLRhKZ1JZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=b8a8831f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1545795482635%26issue%3D20181226&h=07a21160\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1545795482635&amp;issue=20181226</a><br />\n<br />\n【撈底機會】特朗普：勿錯過撈底機會<br />\n2018年12月26日<br />\n<br />\n美股道指平安夜大跌，累計4個交易日已跌逾1880點，由高位累跌近19.1%，逼近熊市邊緣，市場將下跌歸咎於貿易戰，以及近期美國政局混亂所致。不過，作為引起問題的核心，美國總統特朗普則指，現時是撈底的機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，特朗普隔晚在白宮對記者說：「我們擁有世界上最偉大的公司，他們的表現非常出色。他們有創紀錄的數字。我認為現在是一個巨大的購買機會。真的是很好的進場機會。」。"},{"pid":"cb50589c709b07c9affdea4344baaa3c16556472","tid":956124,"uid":54870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:38:02.000Z","msg":"美期仲未止瀉，dow跌緊成舊水<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OobORnd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOobORnd.jpg&h=97284508&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"31446721bd9e0130617501fc6a1d17b4fa5c6509","tid":956124,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T04:38:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8fa93cac27275075392cc14fdc998471648bc9b","tid":956124,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0